NAME
  adoc - generate Markdown API docs from Lua source

SYNOPSIS
  adoc <file.lua> [-o out.md] [--title NAME] [--all]

DESCRIPTION
  Parses a Lua file, finds its function definitions and pairs each with the
  comment block immediately above it, emitting a Markdown reference. By default
  only table members (the public API) are documented; --all includes locals.

OPTIONS
  -o FILE       write to FILE instead of stdout
  --title NAME  document title (defaults to the file name)
  --all         include private/local functions

EXAMPLES
  adoc /lib/json.lua
  adoc mylib.lua -o docs/mylib.md --title "My Library"
